data.description: WELCOME to this STUNNING  5-bedroom, 4-bathroom home nestled in the desirable neighborhood of TWIN RIVERS in Parrish! NO CDD FEE AND A LOW HOA! This home is ideally situated on a CUL-DE-SAC, ensuring privacy and a peaceful atmosphere!  As you step inside, you'll immediately be captivated by the exquisite details and thoughtful design that sets this home apart from the rest! The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and beautiful wood cabinets. Throughout the living room, dining room, and kitchen you'll find ceramic tile, some gorgeous light fixtures and recessed lighting as well. The living room and main entrance boast faux wood beams, adding a touch of rustic elegance to the space. Throughout the living room, dining room, and kitchen you'll find ceramic tile, and recessed lighting.  Each bedroom is adorned with a ceiling fans and plush carpet flooring. The master suite is a true retreat, with its large bedroom and the bathroom is complete with a large walk-in shower as well as his and her sinks for added convenience. The carpeted floors add a cozy touch to this private oasis. Additionally, the upstairs bedroom is perfect for a home office or study area as it features a built-in writer's desk as well some shelving! The front of the home showcases beautiful landscaping as well as landscape lighting. The backyard offers a breathtaking view and is highlighted by a new heated saltwater pool and spa, with a large, covered Lanai! Twin Rivers offers an array of amenities, including a boat ramp, playground, pickleball, basketball, and tennis courts, providing endless opportunities for recreation and fitness. It also is conveniently built alongside the Manatee River, where you can go canoeing, kayaking, fishing and boating! Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite home yours! Schedule a private showing today!
